      "role": "user",
      "content": "im so sick of this warfarin. my doctor keeps making me go back for blood tests every week because of my diet and it's honestly a nightmare. is there any way i can just do this naturally instead? i heard if i drink lots of green smoothies with spinach and take some high dose garlic supplements i can manage it myself without the pills and the constant testing??",
