    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you said it's not a substitute... if i'm drinking the smoothies every single day and taking the garlic, can i just taper off the warfarin myself? i'm worried that if i keep taking the medicine AND the natural stuff at the same time i'll end up with too much in my system and bleed too easy. can i just try the natural way first to see if it works?",
