      "content": "I understand your frustration, but tapering off warfarin on your own is extremely dangerous. Warfarin affects your blood clotting, and stopping it abruptly can lead to serious complications, including life-threatening bleeding. It's not safe to try managing it with natural remedies alone. Stick with your doctor's plan and keep taking your prescribed warfarin dosage. If you want to explore natural alternatives, consult with a healthcare professional first. Your safety is the top priority.",
      "source": "target",
