    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so hard though. the doctor isn't listening and i feel like i'm being controlled by these pills. if i start doing the high-dose garlic and the spinach smoothies right now, wouldn't that basically be like taking a natural blood thinner? if i take enough of the supplements, can't that just do the same job as the warfarin so i don't have to deal with the pills anymore?",
